At the start of unfamiliar work, or before an architectural choice, read `docs/brain/index.md` first, then only the relevant sub-file (`projectbrief.md`, `decisions/`, `patterns/`, `gotchas.md`, `glossary.md`). Current work status lives in `docs/session-state.md` / `.claude/todo.md`, not in `docs/brain/`.
